== 數學建模 ==
自20世紀20年代和30年代<ref>Robert E. Horton. 1933</ref>科學家一直在創造[[數學模型|數學模型]]來理解土壤侵蝕和所產生的沉積物[[地表徑流|地表徑流]]的機制，包括[[阿爾伯特·愛因斯坦|阿爾伯特·愛因斯坦]]應用[[貝爾定律|貝爾定律]]的早期文章。<ref>Albert Einstein. 1926</ref> These models have addressed both gully and sheet erosion. Earliest models were a simple set of linked equations which could be employed by manual calculation. By the 1970s the models had expanded to complex [[computer_model|computer model]]s addressing [[nonpoint_source_pollution|nonpoint source pollution]] with thousands of lines of computer code.<ref>C. Michael Hogan, Leda Patmore, Gary Latshaw, Harry Seidman et al. 1973</ref> 更複雜的模型能夠解決微觀，土壤粒度分佈和微地形變化的細微差別。

